    "question": "How do you say 'I would like a coffee, please' in Russian?",
    "correctAnswer": "Я бы хотел(а) кофе, пожалуйста. (Ya by khotel(a) kofe, pozhaluysta.)",
    "incorrectAnswers": [
      "Дай мне кофе. (Day mne kofe.)",
      "Кофе сейчас! (Kofe seychas!)",
      "Я пью кофе. (Ya pyu kofe.)"
    ],
    "explanation": "'Ya by khotel(a)' is the polite conditional 'I would like'. Add -a for female speaker.",
